## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="fd52f-118">Wartość domyślna to Ssl3 &#124; Tls &#124; Tls11 &#124; Tls12.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd52f-118">The default value is Ssl3 &#124; Tls &#124; Tls11 &#124; Tls12.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd52f-119">Wersje platformy przed 4.6 obsługują tylko Ssl3 i Tls.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd52f-119">Versions of the framework prior to 4.6 only support Ssl3 and Tls.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd52f-120">Jeśli nie są one uwzględniane, komunikacji z wcześniejszych wersji platformy nie będzie możliwe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd52f-120">If these are not included, communication with earlier versions of the framework will not be possible.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd52f-121">Określanie Tls11 i/lub Tls12 wyłączyć użycie Ssl3, nawet jeśli została uwzględniona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd52f-121">Specifying Tls11 and/or Tls12 will disable the usage of Ssl3, even if it has been included.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
NetTcpBinding b = new NetTcpBinding();  
b.Security.Mode = SecurityMode.Transport;  
b.Security.Transport.ClientCredentialType = TcpClientCredentialType.Certificate;  
b.Security.Transport.SslProtocols = SslProtocols.Tls11 | SslProtocols.Tls12;  
EndpointAddress a = new EndpointAddress("net.tcp://contoso.com/TcpAddress");  
ChannelFactory<ICalculator> cf = new ChannelFactory<ICalculator>(b, a);  
cf.Credentials.ClientCertificate.SetCertificate(  
    StoreLocation.LocalMachine,  
    StoreName.My,  
    X509FindType.FindByThumbprint,  
    "0000000000000000000000000000000000000000");  
```
